For systemd-bootchart, several proc debug interfaces are required in the kernel config:
  CONFIG_SCHEDSTATS  (for /proc/<pid>/schedstat)
  CONFIG_VM_EVENT_COUNTERS (for /proc/vmstat)
below is optional, for additional info:
  CONFIG_SCHED_DEBUG (for /proc/<pid>/sched)

Files used:

  /proc/vmstat
  /proc/schedstat
  /proc/sys/kernel/random/entropy_avail
  /proc/<pid>/schedstat
  /proc/<pid>/sched
  /proc/<pid>/stat
  /proc/<pid>/task
  /proc/<pid>/task/<tid>/schedstat
  /proc/<pid>/smaps
